<div class="about-us-container">
    <h1 class="aboutTitle">About Us</h1>
    <p>As an avid animal lover, I have always felt a deep connection with pets and their well-being. This passion inspired me to create "Openarms," a platform dedicated to connecting pet parents who need to find new homes for their pets, whether due to breeding, relocation, or rescuing abandoned strays.</p>
    
    <h3 class="aboutTitle">Why Openarms?</h3>
    <p>Often, pet parents face the challenge of caring for multiple pets after breeding or struggle to find new homes for pets they can no longer care for. Similarly, many stray and abandoned pets need loving homes. "Openarms" aims to simplify this process by providing a space where pet parents can easily connect with potential adopters and buyers.</p>
    <p>Our goal is to ensure every pet finds a safe and loving home, and every pet parent can find the support they need.</p>
    
    <h3 class="aboutTitle">My Story</h3>
    <img src="/images/AboutMe.jpg" alt="Your Picture" class="about-us-image">
    <p>I created "Openarms" because I believe in the importance of responsible pet ownership and the joy pets bring to our lives. My journey started with my own experiences of caring for pets and witnessing the struggles others faced in finding homes for their furry friends.</p>
    
